<View xmlns="sap.m" 
    xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout" controllerName="okul.Application.RegisterCheck.controller.RegisterCheck" 
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.sap.com/sapui5/extension/sap.ui.core.CustomData/1" height="100%">
    <Page showHeader="false">
        <l:FixFlex class="fixFlexVertical">
            <l:flexContent>
                <FlexBox class="pageBGImage loginWrapper" direction="Column" height="100%" alignItems="Center" justifyContent="Center">
                    <items>
                        <FlexBox class="login-content" direction="Column" alignItems="Center" justifyContent="Stretch">
                            <items>
                                <VBox alignItems="Stretch" justifyContent="Stretch" height="100%" width="100%">
                                    <VBox class="login-header" alignItems="Center" justifyContent="Center">
                                        <HBox class="logo-text-wrapper">
                                            <Text text="Aktivitasyon Kodu"/>
                                        </HBox>
                                    </VBox>
                                    <VBox class="login-items-content" alignItems="Center" justifyContent="Stretch" width="100%" height="100%">
                                        <VBox alignItems="Stretch" justifyContent="Start" width="100%">
                                            <Input id="codeInput" type="Text" value=""/>
                                        </VBox>
                                        <HBox>
                                            <Label id="" text="Kalan Zaman"/>
                                            <Label id="lid" text=""/>
                                        </HBox>
                                        <Button text="Tamam" type="Emphasized" press="onPress"/>
                                    </VBox>
                                </VBox>
                            </items>
                        </FlexBox>
                    </items>
                </FlexBox>
            </l:flexContent>
        </l:FixFlex>
    </Page>
</View>
